    "\n",
    "$$\n",
    "J(W,b) = -\\frac{1}{m}\\sum_{i=1}^{m}\\sum_{k=1}^{K} Y_{i,k}\\log(\\hat{Y}_{i,k}) + \\frac{\\lambda}{2}\\|W\\|_2^2\n",
